HubSpot,is,an,internet,company,that,provides,high,quality,internet,marketing,to,small,internet,based,businesses,HubSpot,transforms,relatively,static,small,business,websites,into,modern,marketing,machines,that,produce,the,right,leads,and,helps,convert,a,higher,percentage,of,businesses,into,qualified,opportunities,This,API,lets,developers,specify,a,HubSpot,account,and,access,the,marketing,events,for,that,account,It,also,lets,developers,create,new,marketing,events,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON,It,is,currently,in,alpha,stage